> **Version:** v1.1.0  
> This page documents behavior guaranteed in TealTiger v1.1.0.


# Audit & Redaction

## Goals

- Provide compliance-friendly audit trails
- Prevent sensitive data leakage via logs

## Redaction levels

- NONE (debug only)
- HASH (default)
- SIZE_ONLY
- CATEGORY_ONLY
- FULL

## Default production posture

- input redaction: HASH
- output redaction: HASH
- PII detection: enabled
- debug mode: disabled

```mermaid
flowchart TD
  A[Raw content] --> B[PII detection]
  B --> C[Redaction strategy]
  C --> D[SafeContent fields only]
```
